videos.headline: Hill switches direction for score
videos.description: Kylin Hill makes a move in the backfield on a 6-yard touchdown for Mississippi State to strike first.

videos.headline: Fitzgerald takes it himself into end zone
videos.description: QB Nick Fitzgerald finds a hole and takes it for the score to put Mississippi State up 14-0.

videos.headline: Mississippi State pads lead in final minute of 1st half
videos.description: Nick Fitzgerald finds Deddrick Thomas on a 9-yard touchdown to extend Mississippi State's lead to 21-3 in the final minute of the first half.

videos.headline: Fitzgerald breaks it open on 2nd TD run
videos.description: Nick Fitzgerald squeezes it into the end zone for his second touchdown on the ground, putting Mississippi State up 28-3.

videos.headline: Miss. St. sprints to trophy before time expires
videos.description: Following an on-field brawl, Mississippi State runs to the Golden Egg Trophy before time expires to show it off at midfield in the wake of their victory.
